  [Text] The operations command of the Martyr al-Sadr group 
has issued a statement announcing its forces had attacked the 
headquarters of the Ba'thist 18th Brigade and the headquarters 
of the 215 Artillery Battalion based in the region east of 
Qal'at Salih and that it captured 90 soldiers. The statement 
also said that the attacking forces managed to release 55 
