  [Excerpt] President 'Arafat continued his consultations 
this morning in Tunis within the PLO and with Palestinian 
figures from the occupied territories. 
  These consultations are aimed at forming the transitional 
government of the self-rule in Gaza and Jericho. An official 
Palestinian source told AFP that this government will be 
installed in Jericho on 25 May in accordance with the final 
agreement on self-rule. [passage omitted] 

