<H3> <TI>   Decree Issued on Increase to Heating Allowance </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Decree Issued on Increase to Heating Allowance </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN1205070094 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in 
Arabic 1815 GMT 11 may 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN1205070094 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Text" of Legislative Decree No. 10 issued by President </F>
Hafiz al-Asad on 11 May] 
  [Text] Legislative Decree No. 10 
  President of the Republic, cognizant of the provisions of 
the 
Constitution, decrees the following: 
  Article I: The increase in the heating allowance and the 
price amendments included in Article I of Legislative Decree No. 
5 of 30 April 1994, shall be amended to become 245 lira per 
month, instead of 145 lira per month. Thus, the total of this 
allowance will become 620 lira per month instead 520 lira per 
month. 
  Article II: This legislative decree shall be published in 
the Official Gazette and shall be effective as of 1 May 1994. 
  [Signed] Hafiz al-Asad, president of the Republic, Damascus 
on 1/12/1414 Hegira, corresponding to 11 May 1994 

</TEXT>

