<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] IDF [Israel Defense Forces] soldiers in the Gaza 
Strip apprehended the terrorists who wounded an Israeli truck 
driver near the settlement of Morag today. Our correspondent 
Nisim Qeynan reports that the terrorists overtook the truck and 
opened fire. The driver, who was wounded in the chest and leg, 
was transferred to Soroka Hospital. Following the incident, IDF 
forces sealed off the area, launched a manhunt, and caught the 
terrorists. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

