forces of unity, democracy, and modernization notify brother 
citizens residing in the vicinity of the bloody al-Ahmar gang 
and their supporters in Sanaa, Ta'izz, and al-Hudaydah to 
temporarily vacate in order to avoid injury arising from the 
crimes of the members of this bloody (?killer) family that 
ignited the fires of total war against our people and their 
honorable and loyal forces. The homes of this odious family are 
deemed to be military targets of the forces of unity, democracy, 
and modernization. The members of this family will be pursued, 
wherever they may be. 

