  [Text] Brother Salih Abu-Bakr Bin-Husaynun, minister of oil 
and mineral resources, has conveyed a message from brother 'Ali 
Salim al-Bid, secretary general of the Yemeni Socialist Party 
[YSP] and vice chairman of the Presidential Council, to his 
