latest developments of the situation in Yemen. The message was 
conveyed last night when Shaykh Zayid received brother 
Bin-Husaynun in Abu Dhabi, who confirmed the YSP's stance and 
its complete adherence to the pledge and accord document. 
  For his part, Shaykh Zayid Bin-Sultan Al Nuhayyan again 
stressed the importance of stopping the ongoing fighting in 
Yemen and of resorting to dialogue to reach a political solution 
in order to preserve Yemeni unity in a manner which guarantees 
the interests of the Yemeni people. 

