  [Excerpt] It has been announced today that President Yasir 
'Arafat had issued a decision on 10 December 1993 which 
stipulated the appointment of Major-General (Musbah Hanafi Saqr) 
director of preventive security. 
  WAFA learned that this decision was not made public at the 
