<H3> <TI>   'Arafat Declares Fridays `Official Public Holiday' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    'Arafat Declares Fridays `Official Public Holiday' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1405174594 Algiers Voice of Palestine in Arabic 1702 GMT 
14 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1405174594 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Voice of Palestine </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Chairman Yasir 'Arafat, chairman of the Palestinian 
national authority, today issued a decision stipulating that 
Friday of each week is to be an official public holiday in 
Palestine. 
  The following is the text of the decision: 
  In accordance with the Executive Committee's decision, and 
according to the prerogatives invested in him, the chairman of 
the Palestinian national authority, chairman of the PLO 
Executive Committee, decides the following: 
  Firstly, Friday of each week to be an official public 
holiday 
in Palestine. 
  Secondly, this decision takes effect as from this date, and 
those involved in implementing it shall be informed. 

</TEXT>

