<H3> <TI>   PLO, European Commission Sign Memo of Understanding </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    PLO, European Commission Sign Memo of Understanding </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1305180394 Algiers Voice of Palestine in Arabic 1702 GMT 
13 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1305180394 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Voice of Palestine </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] At noon today, Brother President Yasir 'Arafat 
met Mr. Marin, vice-president of the European Commission. 
'Arafat reviewed with Mr. Marin the situation and the 
developments in the Palestinian territories, and the means of 
support given by the European Commission to help consolidate the 
foundations of the Palestinian national authority in order to 
set up Palestinian institutions. 
  The Palestinian and European sides signed two memoranda of 
understanding. The first one is related to making available the 
necessary support for elections in the national authority and 
its institutions, and the training of cadres concerned with this 
issue. The second one is related to providing the necessary 
support for the Palestinian police force and security. [passage 
omitted] 

</TEXT>

