<F P=100> Palestinian Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Hamas Reportedly To Cooperate With PLO Police </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Hamas Reportedly To Cooperate With PLO Police </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1505202594 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
First Program Network in Persian 1930 GMT 15 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1505202594 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
First Program Network </F>

<F P=105>  Persian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A spokesman for Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement], 
while pledging to continue the struggle against the occupiers of 
al-Quds [Jerusalem], announced: The combatants of Palestine's 
Islamic Resistance Movement will cooperate with the Palestine 
police in the Gaza and Jericho regions for as long as the laws 
and regulations of this police correspond with the idea ruling 
over this Movement. 

</TEXT>

