<H3> <TI>   IDF Evacuates Division Headquarters in Gaza </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    IDF Evacuates Division Headquarters in Gaza </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1605061894 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0600 GMT 16 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1605061894 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The IDF [Israel Defense Forces] evacuated the 
division headquarters in downtown Gaza early this morning. Only 
few installations in the Gaza Strip have still not been handed 
over to the Palestinians. These installations will be evacuated 
today or tonight. The evacuation will be completed tomorrow in 
a ceremony in the Qatif Bloc. Our military affairs 
correspondent Karmela Menashe reports that 24 hours after the 
evacuation is completed the joint IDF and Palestinian police 
patrols will start. 

