<H4>    Aden Reports Sanaa Heavy Losses </H4>

<F P=102> EA1405202694 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
1630 GMT 14 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> EA1405202694 </F>
<F P=104>  Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>
