radio and attributed to a so-called responsible source in the 
Ministry of Defense about the advance of the forces of the 
al-Ahmar gang in many directions, was not based on any truth at 
all. It is just part of the psychological warfare and 
misleading media reporting. It is cheap lies to which the news 
media of the al-Ahmar gang had become accustomed. It is a gang 
headed by a man who is not restrained by anyone. [passage 
omitted] 

