  [Text] Secessionist fortifications in the al-Dali' area 
were blown up the day before yesterday [14 May]. Their 
destruction was attended by a large number of people who 
announced their rejection of the despotic and secessionist gang 
that ruled tyrannically over the people of al-Dali' throughout 
the period of the abominable totalitarian rule. 
  Many people arrived in al-Dali' city declaring their support 
for the legitimate authority. They also declared that they were 
joining with the forces of constitutional legitimacy that have 
returned life to normal and provided them with all means of 
security and protection from any threat posed by the remnants of 
secession and apostasy, which have been completely uprooted from 
the region. 

