Warren Christopher and the accompanying delegation arrived in 
Damascus on a visit to the Syrian Arab Republic. He was 
received at Damascus International Airport by Foreign Minister 
Faruq al-Shar', the head of the United States department at the 
Foreign Ministy, the Syrian ambassador in Washington, and the 
U.S. ambassador in Damascus. 

</TEXT>

