<H3> <TI>   Security Officials Arrive in Territories </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Security Officials Arrive in Territories </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1705191194 Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network 
