  [Excerpt] Muhammad Dahlan and Jibril al-Rujjub arrived 
this evening in the territories. They will head the security 
apparatus in the Gaza Strip and the West Bank. Dahlan, one of 
the founders of the Fatah Hawks in Gaza, fled the territories 
and headed the Gaza Committee in Tunis. Rujjub, 42, who headed 
the West Bank Committee in Tunis, arrived from Jordan and will 
head the security apparatus in the West Bank. [passage omitted] 

