<H3> <TI>   British Ambassador Delivers Message to 'Arafat </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    British Ambassador Delivers Message to 'Arafat </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1705181294 Algiers Voice of Palestine in Arabic 1702 GMT 
17 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1705181294 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Voice of Palestine </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The brother President 'Arafat received today His 
Excellency the British Ambassador to Tunisia Sir Michael Tait, 
who delivered to him a message from British Foreign Secretary 
Douglas Hurd. 
  The meeting was an opportunity, during which the brother 
president reviewed with the ambassador the latest developments 
at the Palestinian scene in light of the signing of the 
agreement of implementing the self-rule in the Gaza sector and 
Jericho. 
  The meeting was attended by brothers Nabil Sha'th and Dr. 
Sami Musallam. 

</TEXT>

