  [Text] A resident of Gaza's al-Rumayl neighborhood was 
killed yesterday. Our correspondent Nisim Qeynan reports 
terrorists fired shots at an IDF [Israel Defense Forces] outpost 
in the city, and the soldiers returned the fire, aiming mainly 
in the air. Military sources say the man was apparently killed 
by the terrorists' fire. 

