<H4>    Headquarters Active Despite Restrictions </H4>

<F P=102> LD1605120294 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
First Program Network in Persian 0930 GMT 16 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1605120294 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
First Program Network </F>

<F P=105>  Persian </F>


