<H3> <TI>   Presidential Council Member Meets Hughes </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Presidential Council Member Meets Hughes </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN1605175094 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
1700 GMT 16 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN1605175094 </F>
<F P=104>  Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Presidential Council member brother 'Abd-al-'Aziz 
'Abd-al-Ghani received U.S. Ambassador in Sanaa Arthur Hughes at 
his office today. 
  During the meeting, the two sides reviewed developments in 
the Yemeni arena, in addition to relations of cooperation 
between the two friendly countries. They also exchanged views 
on several issues of joint interest to our country and the 
United States. 

</TEXT>

